{
  "stem": "1736.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 490.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "If you were caught, you were just sent back and then you either went to camp, or you-- or you got away and you tried again.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyway, we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we lived under very hard circumstances in the woods.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, sometimes with potato peels, whatever the farmers used to throw out, and--",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 112,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And other times, tree barks and-- whatever it was that we could find.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 113,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yes, it was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 114,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was, because this was December and we didn't arrive till late January in-- on-- to the other side, which was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, he was with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Anyway, as we were crossing the border, the time came to-- to go, because it's impossible to just sit there and wait.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We managed to get across the German border and the German guards woke up that something was moving and suddenly, they started shooting.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, this was the middle of the night and-- I can only describe it this way.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were on a narrow icy path with a sheer cliff wall on the left side, narrow path, and an abyss on the other side.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were walking in one line.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they started shooting.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We started not running but going very fast.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the narrow path was very covered in ice and that, and a fellow, not immediately in front of me, but two in front of me, slipped.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, at least I think he slipped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was either slipped or he was shot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 115,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know, but he fell.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 116,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Germans.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He fell.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The fellow behind him tried to get hold of him and got caught up with him, and the two of them just disappeared in front of me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 117,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know why but we-- I just kept walking.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
